headline: Keurig Dr Pepper Stock Outlook: Is Wall Street Bullish or Bearish?
summary: While Keurig Dr Pepper has lagged behind the broader market over the past year, Wall Street analysts maintain a moderately optimistic outlook on the stock’s prospects.
